Friday 3/6/15: Algebraic formula for stereographic projection in the 2 dimensional case: F:S<sup>2</sup> \ {N} --> R<sup>2</sup>, F(x,y,z)=(x,y)/(1-z), F<sup>-1</sup>(u,v)=(2u,2v,u<sup>2</sup>+v<sup>2</sup>-1)/(u<sup>2</sup>+v<sup>2</sup>+1).
<br>
<br>
Wednesday 3/4/15: Stereographic projection. Algebraic formula for stereographic projection in the 1 dimensional case: F:S<sup>1</sup> \ {N} --> R, F(x,y)=x/(1-y), F<sup>-1</sup>(t)=(2t,t<sup>2</sup>-1)/(t<sup>2</sup>+1).
