Friday 2/27/15: The isometries of the sphere are obtained by restricting isometries of R<sup>3</sup> fixing the origin. Geometric description of the resulting isometries from the viewpoint of the sphere.
<br>
<br>
Wednesday 2/25/15: Examples continued: explicit change of basis calculation. Isometries of the sphere.
<br>
<br>
Monday 2/23/15: Examples computed using method developed on Friday 2/20.
