Friday 4/26/13. Let L<sub>1</sub> and L<sub>2</sub> be two hyperbolic lines meeting in a point P in H at angle t. Then the composition R<sub>2</sub>oR<sub>1</sub> is a hyperbolic rotation{&infin;} with center the point P through angle 2t. 
