Wednesday 2/27/13. Rotations in R<sup>2</sup> via multiplication of complex numbers. For complex numbers z,w we have |zw|=|z||w| and arg(zw)=arg(z)+arg(w).
The formula e<sup>it</sup> = cos t + i sin t. The quaternions. Multiplication law. Relation to dot product and cross product of vectors in R<sup>3</sup>.
